# Advanced Password Strength Checker

Welcome to Week 1 of my **#52Weeks52CyberProjects** challenge!  
This project is a Python-based password strength checker that evaluates password security using entropy, character diversity, and common password detection.

##  Features
-  Checks for uppercase, lowercase, digits, and special characters
-  Estimates entropy and rates password strength
-  Flags common passwords using a customizable wordlist (`common.txt`)
-  Provides actionable feedback to improve weak passwords

